div.span:
Prometheus
Metrics Collection:
- Service Availability
- Request Rate
- Latency (p50, p95, p99)
- Model Performance

Grafana Dashboard
- Uptime Charts
- Model Quality (WTR)
- Data Drift (PSI)
- Alert Rules

Kafka Topics
- Predictions Log
- Model Feedback
- Training Data

Deployment Controller
Replicas: 5
Strategy: RollingUpdate
maxUnavailable: 1
maxSurge: 1

Pod Disruption Budget
minAvailable: 4
Ensures high availability

ReplicaSet Controller
Maintains 5 pods
Auto-restarts failed pods

Symlink-based Versioning
/home/mlprod/models/latest v{timestamp}
Model artifacts (28MB ALS, user/movie maps)
Provenance manifests with SHA256

Startup Probe
GET /health/live
Initial: 20s, Period: 5s
Fail threshold: 12
Timeout: 5s

Liveness Probe
GET /health/live
Initial: 30s, Period: 10s
Fail threshold: 3
Timeout: 5s
Action: Restart pod

Readiness Probe
GET /health/ready
Initial: 30s, Period: 5s
Fail threshold: 2
Timeout: 5s
Action: Remove from service
